<body><bold>Chitin Leggings<end>
<tab><RECIPE name=chitinLeggings domain=Hivetera>
To protect their legs from the stray arrow-in-the-thigh, the nomads had to come up with some sort of leg armor. The idea to use chitin plates to make leggings came from someone who had stayed in a mud bath too long, and the mud hardened to their legs. This is the reason why you should never sit to long in a mud bath...

